Union MaybeI32 has none; some value: i32.

To make maybe flag: i1, giving MaybeI32.
Give MaybeI32.some with value be 42 when flag; otherwise MaybeI32.none.

To value or zero maybe: MaybeI32, giving i32.
Give match maybe:
MaybeI32.some with value gives value;
otherwise gives 0.

To main, giving i32.
Let maybe be make maybe true.
Give value or zero maybe.
